{"tid":1558670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"燒山唔會攬炒, 只會益林鄭","createTime":"2019-09-10T14:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T16:15:55.000Z","uid":128522,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"410be54abed32369c2b67e3c551db2593121c919","tid":1558670,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:12:27.000Z","msg":"首先, <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">政府想毀滅郊野公園好耐</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家有人想幫佢做埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n燒完山環評就寫生態價值極低<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又可以起樓比新移民住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外, 毀滅埋水塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n郊野公園附近就係水塘<br />\n無左郊野公園, 就可以用水質會受污染做借口<br />\n廢左個水塘,<br />\n變相廢埋你香港食水自給自足既能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又可以屈係抗爭者做恐怖份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 又可以斷你水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府何樂而不為?<br />\n<br />\n核彈都唔割<br />\n唔係比你濫用黎做D唔係對準政權既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁多竇你唔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 你走去burnhill? <br />\n你話唔係對家做我都唔信囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同比個正皮我"},{"pid":"d98adadc7da9e4ff44a42a592b8676c97fad87ea","tid":1558670,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:12:43.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"04411572212c1d448b49769447d10fce8c8c7037","tid":1558670,"uid":73856,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:13:59.000Z","msg":"政府自己派人燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bdfee6da688d9e8139bcc4b2a7eec8e12c2cbd","tid":1558670,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dis